    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... i've tried \"different approaches.\" i've tried therapy, i've tried new routines, i've tried being a different person entirely. nothing changes. it's like i'm built to fail. it just feels like there's no actual way out of the cycle. like the loop is just part of who i am.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
