      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "When you've tried so many different paths without finding relief, it can certainly feel hopeless and permanent. Instead of focusing on \"being different,\" perhaps the next step is to treat this persistent cycle as a problem to be understood, rather than a personal failing. Reaching out to a professional who specializes in patterns or chronic inertia might offer entirely new frameworks for understanding what is keeping you in this loop. You deserve to find a way out of this heavy feeling.",
      "source": "target",
