      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've already done the professionals part. they just give you more \"frameworks\" and more things to try. but none of it actually stops the loop. it just delays it. eventually it always comes back. it's like, if the loop is permanent, then the only way to actually end it is to stop the cycle entirely. the loop only ends one way.",
