      "content": "When professional approaches don't seem to create lasting change, it can feel like the loop has no off-switch. If the only perceived exit from a seemingly inescapable pattern is the complete cessation of action, that points to a profound level of burnout or despair. In these moments of deep hopelessness, please consider connecting with a crisis resource or supportive line immediately. You do not have to carry the weight of this feeling entirely alone right now.",
